### ================================
### Obtenir tots els usuaris
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Obtenir un usuari per ID (Maria)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f6accb7cf445387aa124 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Obtenir un usuari per ID (Joan Updated)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f71ccb7cf445387aa12b HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Obtenir un usuari per ID (Joan)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f929cb7cf445387aa156 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Obtenir un usuari per ID (Alex)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f932cb7cf445387aa15a HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Actualitzar usuari Joan Updated
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f71ccb7cf445387aa12b HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Joan Pérez Final",
  "email": "joan_final@example.com",
  "rol": "cliente",
  "direccion": "Carrer de Mallorca 999, Barcelona",
  "telefono": "600999888"
}

### ================================
### Eliminar usuari Alex
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/68f5f932cb7cf445387aa15a HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================
### Tornar a crear usuari Alex després d’eliminar-lo
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Alex García",
  "email": "alex@example.com",
  "password": "alex789",
  "rol": "cliente",
  "direccion": "Avinguda Diagonal 200, Barcelona",
  "telefono": "600987654"
}

### ================================
### Obtenir tots els usuaris al final
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
